            <p>Zend_Form, Element, and DisplayGroup all now have a 'setDisableTranslator()' method (and corresponding config key 'disableTranslator') that allows you to disable translations for that item (setting it on the form will disable for the entire form).</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
